{"about_the_game":"Embark on the exciting adventure in a unique blend of story-driven and third-person adventure  game set in an alternate universe dominated by church and its sisters.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650910/extras/output14.gif?t=1662374524\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> THE STORY </h2>Sisterhood is one of many church congregations. <br>You play as one of the sisters, involved in special operations. <br>Complete missions, rescue sisters from troubles, gain their affection and unlock interactions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> MAGIC ESSENCE </h2>Magic essence that can be harvested from demonic activity and used for healing.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> CORRUPTION </h2>Demonic activity causes corruption which is toxic for all humans, however sisters armor has powerful protection against corruption.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> SUMMON</h2>Sisters have the ability to summon fellow sisters and creatures to help them on their mission.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> FEATURES </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Character Customization Options<br></li><li> Interactions with fellow sisters - gaining their affection and unlocking interactions.<br></li><li> Environment with dynamic weather, daytime and the world itself.<br></li><li> Story-driven adventure with combat and exploration</li></ul><br>Sisterhood is built around weapons and precision in using them. Finding enemy weak spots plays a vital role in successful combat and achieving ultimate victory.<br><br>Fighting mechanics aimed at precision in landing headshots in crucial to your survival<br><br>Multiple world bosses and gameplay aimed at finding enemy weakness, designed to be challenging and rewarding.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650910/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1662374524","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650910/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1662374524","capsule_image":"https: